&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimization Techniques:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of Transformer architectures and LLM/VLM/Diffusion model optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of inference optimization, such as workload scheduling, CUDA graph, compiled, efficient kernels&lt;/li&gt;
