&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our product surface is expanding fast - GPU clusters, managed storage, networking, and observability - and we&#39;re adding a Product Manager to the Together Cloud team to own the day-to-day product work that keeps these AI infrastructure products moving. You&#39;ll start across the full surface, with an early focus on observability and GPU Clusters, partnering closely with engineering to ship the feature work that customers feel every day.&lt;/p&gt;
