&lt;li&gt;Comfortable operating cross-functionally with Sales, Product, and Engineering to align market strategy with execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional analytical skills with a data-driven approach to decision-making and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in engineering and MBA preferre&lt;/li&gt;
